What a surprise! From the look on the outside, you would not expect to get the level of cuisine presented at this restaurant. It's a little bitty hole in the wall nestled between two other grocery stores right off of 167th street. If you blink you may pass it by. But try not to. The tacos here were excellent and made to order. The ingredients tasted fresh and the service was spectacular. Try their food with their red sauce. It's a fun spicy blend that makes your meat sing.
